<template>
  <el-container>
    <!-- 头部区域 -->
    <el-header><el-button type="info" @click="logout">退出</el-button>Header</el-header>
   <!-- 页面主题区域 -->
   <el-container>
      <el-aside width="200px">Aside</el-aside>
      <el-main>Main</el-main>
    </el-container>

</template>

<script>
export default {
  methods: {
    logout() {
      window.sessionStorage.clear()
      this.$router.push('/login')
    },
  },
}
</script>

</style>
